  <summary>Used with the <command tag="sort">sort</command> <glossary tag="command">command</glossary>, <function tag="number">number</function> <control_st tag="function">function</control_st>, and <operator tag="is among">is among</operator> and <operator tag="is not among">is not among</operator> <glossary tag="operator">operators</glossary> to designate each <keyword tag="character">character</keyword> as a separate portion of a <keyword tag="string">string</keyword>.  Also used with the <command tag="find">find</command> <glossary tag="command">command</glossary> to search for a string of characters.</summary>
